---
import {
  Description,
  InfoTable,
  InfoTableBody,
  InfoTableCell,
  InfoTableCellHead,
  InfoTableHead,
  InfoTableRow,
  PageleteSection,
  SectionHeader,
} from "components";

import { topics } from "../static";
---

<PageleteSection>
  <SectionHeader id={topics.typescale.id}>
    {topics.typescale.title}
  </SectionHeader>

  <Description>
    Neo uses a different font depending on the language. For Avayaâ€™s officially
    supported languages, Neo uses the Noto Sans JP font provided by Google. This
    ensures that the font is legible to all users, and provides a character set
    for various languages for free. Noto Sans JP has been tested for use in
    multiple languages, and satisfies the WCAG regulations for accessibility.
  </Description>

  <Description>
    This interactive table shows how the fonts are displayed with regard to
    size, weight, and style. Use the design tokens to ensure the correct values
    are employed. If you need a language that is not listed, please reach out to
    us for guidance.
  </Description>

  <InfoTable>
    <InfoTableHead>
      <InfoTableRow>
        <InfoTableCellHead>Type</InfoTableCellHead>
        <InfoTableCellHead>Examples</InfoTableCellHead>
      </InfoTableRow>
    </InfoTableHead>

    <InfoTableBody>
      <InfoTableRow>
        <InfoTableCell>H1 - Noto Sans, 44px (Regular and Bold)</InfoTableCell>
        <InfoTableCell>
          <h1>The quick brown fox...</h1>
        </InfoTableCell>
      </InfoTableRow>

      <InfoTableRow>
        <InfoTableCell>
          H2 - Noto Sans, 32px (Regular, Bold and Underline)
        </InfoTableCell>
        <InfoTableCell>
          <h2>The quick brown fox jumps over the lazy dog</h2>
        </InfoTableCell>
      </InfoTableRow>

      <InfoTableRow>
        <InfoTableCell>H3 - Noto Sans, 26px (Regular)</InfoTableCell>
        <InfoTableCell>
          <h3>The quick brown fox jumps over the lazy dog</h3>
        </InfoTableCell>
      </InfoTableRow>

      <InfoTableRow>
        <InfoTableCell>H4 - Noto Sans, 19px (Regular)</InfoTableCell>
        <InfoTableCell>
          <h4>The quick brown fox jumps over the lazy dog</h4>
        </InfoTableCell>
      </InfoTableRow>

      <InfoTableRow>
        <InfoTableCell>Large Body - Noto Sans, 16px (Regular)</InfoTableCell>
        <InfoTableCell>
          <p class="neo-body-large">
            The quick brown fox jumps over the lazy dog
          </p>
        </InfoTableCell>
      </InfoTableRow>

      <InfoTableRow>
        <InfoTableCell>
          Body - Noto Sans, 14px (Regular, Italic, Underline and Semibold and
          Uppercase)
        </InfoTableCell>
        <InfoTableCell>
          <p>The quick brown fox jumps over the lazy dog</p>
        </InfoTableCell>
      </InfoTableRow>

      <InfoTableRow>
        <InfoTableCell>Body Code - Roboto Mono, 14px (Regular)</InfoTableCell>
        <InfoTableCell>
          <p style={{ fontFamily: "Roboto Mono" }}>
            The quick brown fox jumps over the lazy dog
          </p>
        </InfoTableCell>
      </InfoTableRow>

      <InfoTableRow>
        <InfoTableCell>
          Small Body - Noto Sans, 12px (Regular and Light)
        </InfoTableCell>
        <InfoTableCell>
          <p class="neo-body-small">
            The quick brown fox jumps over the lazy dog
          </p>
        </InfoTableCell>
      </InfoTableRow>

      <InfoTableRow>
        <InfoTableCell>
          Tiny Body - Noto Sans, 10px (Regular and Light)
        </InfoTableCell>
        <InfoTableCell>
          <p class="neo-body-tiny">
            The quick brown fox jumps over the lazy dog
          </p>
        </InfoTableCell>
      </InfoTableRow>
    </InfoTableBody>
  </InfoTable>
</PageleteSection>
